name: Factory Defect • SPECIAL EDITION • Galactic Abductees • Series 02 • Woodland Fae-Hominids of Milmion - Ava Carren Original-Captive Edition® • Limited 10 PCS
description: After days of rendering, a flaw was discovered in this animated special edition boxed toy from Optera's Galactic Abductees series 02. A close look at the rear of the bonus fairy reveals the glitch. Rather than discard the product entirely, it's being made available exclusively at HEN for those who would like to own a Galactic Abductees SPECIAL EDITION but ordinarily could never hope to afford one. Note the genuine, glitch-free 1 of 1 SPECIAL EDITION Ava Carren will eventually be included in the official collection at rarible.com/galacticabductees.
